{"tid":258214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"洪欣網上開火","createTime":"2017-05-26T02:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T01:05:35.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35f368e66a81eb2d769b970f9fe554c6a04e3f92","tid":258214,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:01:47.000Z","msg":"洪欣雖然幫莫少聰生下小朋友，但最後兩人都是分手收場。仔仔已經16歲，兩個竟然仍然好好火，上年二人就隔住微博互寸，好明顯再見不是朋友。上年10月莫少聰不忿長年被洪欣粉絲網上攻擊，在微博po上當年抱住剛出世兒子莫鎬濂的相片，更留言求放過。<br />\n<br />\n他說︰「請你捫心自問，當年的事真的錯的都在我嗎? 我沉默不代表我不敢說。」弄得李嘉欣留言鬧爆︰「人家四口家庭現在很幸福，你的不幸為什麼要把洪欣拉下水，你吃白粉都是洪欣叫你去的嗎? 你自找的一切 為什現在要來怨人。」<br />\n至於一路湊大兒子的洪欣，09年同細自己11年的內地演員，張丹峰結婚之後生下女兒曦彤，一家四口好開心。在莫少聰發文六日後，洪欣終於在微博留言︰「莫先生說實話我沒有留意你的新聞，怎樣可能找水軍去攻擊，一個我已經遺忘了的人呢?」真係遍地花生。"},{"pid":"9767ec7c0b93dc687d86bdb82107a54fda8a3355","tid":258214,"uid":53784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:02:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></span>"},{"pid":"2a148e6b5d149b7e7936ce619ecabee4ae81c1bb","tid":258214,"uid":42661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真</span></span>"},{"pid":"d2bb383c3b3d4e461d717dda8d98441728fb2660","tid":258214,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係</span></span>"},{"pid":"04c3a523c0548102bb94303717a62e7e1282a065","tid":258214,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:34:06.000Z","msg":"連李嘉欣都幫洪欣<br />\n抵俾人屌啦莫生"},{"pid"